title: Bug 121682: Exception when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: Description: An exception is thrown when trying to export data from the attached report.
OB: When trying to export the data from the table, an exception occurs in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.
EB: When exporting the data in the table, the data should be successfully exported without any exceptions being thrown.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Add a table to the report which includes a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row.
2. Preview the attached report.
3. Attempt to export the data from the table.
